summary: The 'dan's been gone because he's gonna post this video' thread
body:
The ‘dan’s been gone because he’s gonna post this video’ thread

If you want, reblog with why you think dan’s not active yet, what video you think he’s gonna come back with and when. I wanna see what people think. Only if you want, of course.

Personally, I think he’s gone because he’s gonna come back with a 2019 top dan memes video in december and he’s just preparing for it, collecting all the I miss dan posts and be kind to dan and phil posts and the memes about that stuff and the messages some people might’ve sent him.
